{"tid":689040,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"唔見左舊台證上唔上到機？","createTime":"2018-06-03T18:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T08:49:27.000Z","uid":26372,"like":0,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a15997e39ae7677c86723a43da37df6394602378","tid":689040,"uid":26372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T18:34:05.000Z","msg":"唔係香港出世，之前去過台灣，諗住搞網上簽證<br />\n上網見到話「非香港澳門出生者，請帶備曾經赴台之入臺證正本，以便航空公司查驗。」<br />\n但舊個張已經唔見左 上網又見到有啲人話唔駛帶 係落地簽證先要<br />\n請問有無地勤巴絲或者曾經遇過差唔多情況嘅巴絲，知道到底航空公司同埋台灣入境嗰邊需唔需要檢查舊台證？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為如果需要就要當第一次去咁重新搞過張"},{"pid":"9a7791d10b5e0ed3606d8944d162d5e83fb94953","tid":689040,"uid":30107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T18:48:50.000Z","msg":"如果你係拎香港特別行政區簽證身份書(DI)去過台灣 而你依家拎香港特區護照 就要去力寶中心台經辦到整多次入台証，如果你之前係用特區護區去過可以係網上整入台証，個岀世地一定要填啱"},{"pid":"9abb1315f3c05135bc0b7e0f568c30b81edd9515","tid":689040,"uid":9127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a7791d10b5e0ed3606d8944d162d5e83fb94953","tid":689040,"uid":30107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T18:48:50.000Z","msg":"如果你係拎香港特別行政區簽證身份書(DI)去過台灣 而你依家拎香港特區護照 就要去力寶中心台經辦到整多次入台証，如果你之前係用特區護區去過可以係網上整入台証，個岀世地一定要填啱"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T18:59:35.000Z","msg":"而家力寶無得做單次入台證啦<br />\n全部變曬網上做<br />\n<a href=\"https://niioa.immigration.gov.tw/NIA_OnlineApply_inter/visafreeApply/visafreeApplyForm.action\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fniioa.immigration.gov.tw%2FNIA_OnlineApply_inter%2FvisafreeApply%2FvisafreeApplyForm.action&d=LzoM0JrnwE7uq8%2BNdr6xi8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=b5226548\" target=\"_blank\">https://niioa.immigration.gov.tw/NIA_OnlineApply_inter/visafreeApply/visafreeApplyForm.action</a>"},{"pid":"39c0c90cb5e617670d5159fddcee81e90b8b3673","tid":689040,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T19:01:19.000Z","msg":"第一次特登搞咗